## Overview

This portfolio was designed and built from scratch to present my work and skills to potential employers and collaborators. It combines a clean editorial aesthetic (Playfair Display + Inter) with a warm terracotta accent palette and is fully responsive across all screen sizes.

---

## Sections Implemented

### 1.  Navigation Bar
- Sticky top navbar with blur/glass effect using `backdrop-filter`
- Smooth scroll links to all sections
- Fully responsive with Bootstrap's hamburger collapse on mobile
- Animated underline hover effect on nav links

### 2.  Hero Section
- Full-viewport background image with dark gradient overlay
- Name, role subtitle, and two CTA buttons ("View My Work" / "Get in Touch")
- Responsive typography using `clamp()` for fluid font sizing

### 3.  About Me
- Two-column card layout: profile sidebar + bio panel
- Circular profile photo with accent border
- Detail list: name, profile, phone, email
- Skills badges grid (HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, JavaScript, Python, Django, SQL, Tableau, Power BI, PostgreSQL, Git)
- Meta grid: location, availability status (with live green dot), focus area, project count

### 4. Projects
- Responsive 3-column card grid (collapses to 1 on mobile)
- Each card includes: screenshot, tech stack label, title, description, live site link, GitHub link
- Six projects showcased (see [Projects Featured](#projects-featured))
- Hover lift effect on cards

### 5. Contact
- Social icon row: GitHub, LinkedIn, Email
- Contact form with fields: Email, Name, Subject, Message
- Accent-coloured focus ring on inputs
- Bootstrap's `novalidate` form with required field attributes

### 6. Footer
- Simple dark footer with portfolio credit line

