## Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| Markup | HTML5 (semantic elements) |
| Styling | CSS3 custom properties, Flexbox, CSS Grid |
| Framework | Bootstrap 5.3.3 |
| Icons | Bootstrap Icons 1.11.3 |
| Fonts | Google Fonts — Playfair Display, Inter |
| Hosting | GitHub Pages |

