## Bonus Features

- **Print stylesheet** — the `@media print` rule hides nav, hero, projects, and contact sections, leaving only the About card formatted cleanly for printing as a résumé
- **Skip link** — a visually hidden "Skip to main content" link appears on keyboard focus for screen reader and keyboard accessibility
- **Reduced motion support** — all transitions and animations are disabled for users who prefer reduced motion (`prefers-reduced-motion: reduce`)
- **`aria-label` attributes** — icon-only buttons (GitHub, code links) have descriptive aria-labels for screen readers
- **Fluid typography** — `clamp()` is used throughout so headings scale smoothly between mobile and desktop without breakpoint jumps
- **CSS custom properties** — the entire colour palette and font stack is defined as tokens in `:root`, making theming straightforward
- **`available-dot` indicator** — a pure-CSS animated green dot signals availability status without any JavaScript

